#: .\makeshift-still.json
msgid "makeshift still"
msgstr "临时蒸馏器"

#. ~ Description for makeshift still
#: .\makeshift-still.json
msgid ""
"Little more than two bottles buried in dirt with a bent metal sheet to "
"condense evaporated liquids. Will serve as a still in a pinch."
msgstr "不过是两个埋在土里的瓶子，加上一块弯曲的金属板来冷凝蒸发的液体。紧急情况下可作为蒸馏器使用。"

