msgid_plural "apple tree cuttings"
msgstr[0] "苹果树插条"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'apple tree cutting', 'str_pl': 'apple tree
#. cuttings'}
#: .\tree-harvesting.json
msgid ""
"A large cutting from an apple tree. It's advised to pot it in early spring "
"because it will fully grow by the time it can be harvested in autumn. It "
"dies quickly, so hurry and pot it!"
msgstr "一根来自苹果树的大插条。建议在早春将其盆栽，因为它会在秋季可收获时完全长成。它枯萎得很快，所以赶紧盆栽吧！"

