#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid "date tree"
msgstr "椰枣树"

#. ~ Description for date tree
#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid ""
"This is 'Phoenix dactylifera', commonly known as the date palm or even much "
"more commonly as the date tree, belonging to the 'Phoenix' genus, "
"naturalized in many tropical along with subtropical regions worldwide like "
"North Africa, Middle East, South Asia, that has been genetically engineered "
"to withstand New England's four seasons. It bears dates in the summer.  If "
"you examined the branches more closely, you could probably find some mature "
"dates.  You could also cut it down with the right tools."
msgstr ""
"这是'Phoenix "
"dactylifera'，通常被称为枣椰树或更常见的枣树，属于'Phoenix'属，已在全球许多热带和亚热带地区归化，如北非、中东、南亚，并经过基因工程改造以适应新英格兰的四季。它在夏季结枣。如果你更仔细地检查树枝，可能会发现一些成熟的枣子。你也可以用合适的工具砍倒它。"

#. ~ Description for date tree
#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid ""
"This is 'Phoenix dactylifera', commonly known as the date palm or even much "
"more commonly as the date tree, belonging to the 'Phoenix' genus, "
"naturalized in many tropical along with subtropical regions worldwide like "
"North Africa, Middle East, South Asia, that has been genetically engineered "
"to withstand New England's four seasons. It bears dates in the summer.  "
"Looks like all the ripe dates have been picked.  You could also cut it down "
"with the right tools."
msgstr ""
"这是'Phoenix "
"dactylifera'，通常被称为枣椰树或更常见的枣树，属于'Phoenix'属，已在全球许多热带和亚热带地区归化，如北非、中东、南亚，并经过基因工程改造以适应新英格兰的四季。它在夏季结枣。看起来所有成熟的枣子都已被采摘。你也可以用合适的工具砍倒它。"

#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid "fig tree"
msgstr "无花果树"

#. ~ Description for fig tree
#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid ""
"This is 'Ficus carica', commonly known as fig tree, belonging to the 'Ficus'"
" genus, naturalized in many tropical along with subtropical regions like "
"Mediterranean, West Asia, South Asia, which is now widely grown throughout "
"the world, that has been genetically engineered to withstand New England's "
"four seasons. It bears figs in the summer.  If you examined the branches "
"more closely, you could probably find some mature figs.  You could also cut "
"it down with the right tools."
msgstr ""
"这是'Ficus "
"carica'，通常被称为无花果树，属于'Ficus'属，已在许多热带和亚热带地区归化，如地中海、西亚、南亚，现已在全球广泛种植，并经过基因工程改造以适应新英格兰的四季。它在夏季结无花果。如果你更仔细地检查树枝，可能会发现一些成熟的无花果。你也可以用合适的工具砍倒它。"

#. ~ Description for fig tree
#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid ""
"This is 'Ficus carica', commonly known as fig tree, belonging to the 'Ficus'"
" genus, naturalized in many tropical along with subtropical regions like "
"Mediterranean, West Asia, South Asia, which is now widely grown throughout "
"the world, that has been genetically engineered to withstand New England's "
"four seasons. It bears figs in the summer.  Looks like all the ripe figs "
"have been picked.  You could also cut it down with the right tools."
msgstr ""
"这是'Ficus "
"carica'，通常被称为无花果树，属于'Ficus'属，已在许多热带和亚热带地区归化，如地中海、西亚、南亚，现已在全球广泛种植，并经过基因工程改造以适应新英格兰的四季。它在夏季结无花果。看起来所有成熟的无花果都已被采摘。你也可以用合适的工具砍倒它。"

#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid "banana tree"
msgstr "香蕉树"

#. ~ Description for banana tree
#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid ""
"This is 'Musa acuminata', commonly known as banana plants or even much more "
"commonly known as banana trees, belonging to the 'Musa' genus, naturalized "
"in tropical regions of South Asia, Southeast Asia, that has been genetically"
" engineered to withstand New England's four seasons. It bears bananas in the"
" summer.  If you examined the branches more closely, you could probably find"
" some mature bananas.  You could also cut it down with the right tools."
msgstr ""
"这是'Musa "
"acuminata'，通常被称为香蕉植株或更常见的香蕉树，属于'Musa'属，已在南亚、东南亚的热带地区归化，并经过基因工程改造以适应新英格兰的四季。它在夏季结香蕉。如果你更仔细地检查树枝，可能会发现一些成熟的香蕉。你也可以用合适的工具砍倒它。"

#. ~ Description for banana tree
#: .\mapgen\new_trees.json
msgid ""
"This is 'Musa acuminata', commonly known as banana plants or even much more "
"commonly known as banana trees, belonging to the 'Musa' genus, naturalized "
"in tropical regions of South Asia, Southeast Asia, that has been genetically"
" engineered to withstand New England's four seasons. It bears bananas in the"
" summer.  Looks like all the ripe bananas have been picked.  You could also "
"cut it down with the right tools."
msgstr ""
"这是'Musa "
"acuminata'，通常被称为香蕉植株或更常见的香蕉树，属于'Musa'属，已在南亚、东南亚的热带地区归化，并经过基因工程改造以适应新英格兰的四季。它在夏季结香蕉。看起来所有成熟的香蕉都已被采摘。你也可以用合适的工具砍倒它。"

#. ~ Sign
#: .\mapgen\trees_farm_tweaks.json
msgid "<given_name>'s Tree Farm, call us at 555-8758!"
msgstr "<given_name>的树苗农场，请致电555-8758！"

#. ~ Sign
#: .\mapgen\trees_farm_tweaks.json
msgid "Christmas trees available early winter!"
msgstr "圣诞树初冬供应！"

#. ~ Sign
#: .\mapgen\trees_farm_tweaks.json
msgid "We grow tropical, subtropical trees, we even try to grow grapes!"
msgstr "我们种植热带、亚热带树木，甚至尝试种植葡萄！"

#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "giant cockroach nymph"
msgid_plural "giant cockroach nymphs"
msgstr[0] "巨型蟑螂若虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'giant cockroach nymph'}
#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "A baby mutant cockroach about the size of a rat."
msgstr "一只幼年突变蟑螂，大小约如老鼠。"

#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "dermatik larva"
msgid_plural "dermatik larvae"
msgstr[0] "皮蝇幼虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dermatik larva', 'str_pl': 'dermatik larvae'}
#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid ""
"A fat white grub as big as a squirrel, with a pair of large, spadelike "
"mandibles."
msgstr "一条肥硕的白色蛆虫，大小如松鼠，长有一对巨大的铲状颚。"

#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "locust nymph"
msgid_plural "locust nymphs"
msgstr[0] "蝗虫若虫"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'locust nymph'}
#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid ""
"A locust the size of a rabbit.  You'd hate to think what a swarm of these "
"could do."
msgstr "一只兔子大小的蝗虫。你不敢想象一群这样的蝗虫会造成什么破坏。"

#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid "rattlesnake"
msgid_plural "rattlesnakes"
msgstr[0] "响尾蛇"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rattlesnake'}
#: .\mobile\mobile-override-non-mammal.json
msgid ""
"The timber rattlesnake is the most venomous viper native to New England.  "
"Climatic changes have extended its range far into the north."
msgstr "林响尾蛇是新英格兰本土毒性最强的蝰蛇。气候变化已将其活动范围向北大幅扩展。"
